parameters.name: 外部评级等级下调结果值

processors.description: 取‘发布时间’和‘评级’字段进行比对，下调则触发
processors.script:
ESql.withInstance(EngineSpringApplicationContextUtil.getDefaultDataSource()){ sql->
    sql.withTransaction{
        def exe_sql='''
        
INSERT INTO T_AFT_WARN_INFO 
(
ID,                    --ID
RULE_CODE,             --规则编码  
TASK_SEQNO,            --跑批批次
LESSEE_ID,             --承租人ID
ASSO_ID,               --关联人ID
ASSO_TYPE,             --关联人类型
WARN_TIME,             --预警时间
WARN_DESC              --预警详情
)
SELECT
 SYS_GUID() ID  --ID
,'R002007001' RULE_CODE --规则编码
,(SELECT MAX(TASK_SEQNO)+1 FROM T_AFT_WARN_INFO WHERE RULE_CODE='R002007001') TASK_SEQNO --跑批批次
,A.LESSEE_ID --承租人ID
,A.ASSO_ID --关联人ID
,A.ASSO_TYPE --关联人类型
,SYSTIMESTAMP WARN_TIME --预警时间
,'发布时间' || B.PUBLIC_DATE || '，外部评级等级' || B.RATING || '，上次发布时间' || C.PUBLIC_DATE || '，上次等级' || C.RATING  WARN_DESC --预警详情
FROM T_AFT_ATTEN_CUSTOMER A     --客户信息关注表
JOIN 
(         
SELECT DISTINCT company_ID,PUBLIC_DATE,RATING,CASE WHEN RATING='AAA' THEN 1
     WHEN RATING='AA' THEN 2
     WHEN RATING='A' THEN 3
     WHEN RATING='BBB' THEN 4
     WHEN RATING='BB' THEN 5
     WHEN RATING='B+' THEN 6
     WHEN RATING='B' THEN 7
     WHEN RATING='B-' THEN 8
     WHEN RATING='CCC+' THEN 9
     WHEN RATING='CCC' THEN 10
     WHEN RATING='CCC-' THEN 11
     WHEN RATING='CC' THEN 12
     WHEN RATING='C' THEN 13
     WHEN RATING='D' THEN 14 END AS RATING_FLAG FROM (       
  SELECT company_ID,PUBLIC_DATE,RATING,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY company_ID ORDER BY PUBLIC_DATE DESC ) RN 
  FROM FB_RATING_RECORD
  WHERE  TO_CHAR(FD_CREATE_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') =TO_CHAR(SYSDATE,'YYYY-MM-DD')
  AND PUBLIC_DATE IS NOT NULL)
  WHERE RN = 1
  ) B
 ON A.ASSO_COMPANY_ID = B.COMPANY_ID
 JOIN 
(         
SELECT DISTINCT company_ID,PUBLIC_DATE,RATING,CASE WHEN RATING='AAA' THEN 1
     WHEN RATING='AA' THEN 2
     WHEN RATING='A' THEN 3
     WHEN RATING='BBB' THEN 4
     WHEN RATING='BB' THEN 5
     WHEN RATING='B+' THEN 6
     WHEN RATING='B' THEN 7
     WHEN RATING='B-' THEN 8
     WHEN RATING='CCC+' THEN 9
     WHEN RATING='CCC' THEN 10
     WHEN RATING='CCC-' THEN 11
     WHEN RATING='CC' THEN 12
     WHEN RATING='C' THEN 13
     WHEN RATING='D' THEN 14 END AS RATING_FLAG FROM (       
  SELECT company_ID,PUBLIC_DATE,RATING,ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY company_ID ORDER BY PUBLIC_DATE DESC ) RN 
  FROM FB_RATING_RECORD
  WHERE  TO_CHAR(FD_CREATE_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') =TO_CHAR(SYSDATE,'YYYY-MM-DD')
  AND PUBLIC_DATE IS NOT NULL)
  WHERE RN = 2
  ) C
  ON B.COMPANY_ID=C.COMPANY_ID
  AND B.RATING_FLAG > C.RATING_FLAG
  AND A.IS_ATTEN='Y'  
        
        '''.toString();
        sql.execute(exe_sql);
    }
}

parameters.name: 出现失信被执行信息结果值

processors.description: 取失信被执行人接口，记录数加总，取‘做出执行依据单位’和‘发布时间’字段
processors.script:
ESql.withInstance(EngineSpringApplicationContextUtil.getDefaultDataSource()){ sql->
    sql.withTransaction{
        def exe_sql='''
        
INSERT INTO T_AFT_WARN_INFO 
(
ID,                    --ID
RULE_CODE,             --规则编码  
TASK_SEQNO,            --跑批批次
LESSEE_ID,             --承租人ID
ASSO_ID,               --关联人ID
ASSO_TYPE,             --关联人类型
WARN_TIME,             --预警时间
WARN_DESC              --预警详情
)
SELECT
SYS_GUID() ID  --ID
,'R003003001' RULE_CODE --规则编码
,(SELECT MAX(TASK_SEQNO)+1 FROM T_AFT_WARN_INFO WHERE RULE_CODE='R003003001') TASK_SEQNO --跑批批次
,A.LESSEE_ID --承租人ID
,A.ASSO_ID --关联人ID
,A.ASSO_TYPE --关联人类型
,SYSTIMESTAMP WARN_TIME --预警时间
,'案号为'||B.CASE_NUMBER||'，做出执行依据单位为' || B.DECISION_AUTHORITY || '，发布时间为' || B.PUBLIC_DATE|| '，失信被执行人行为具体情形为'||B.EXECUTE_DETAIL || '，生效法律文书确定的义务为'||B.EFFECT_OBLIGATIONS ||'，被执行人的履行情况为'||B.EXECUTION_RESULT  WARN_DESC --预警详情
FROM T_AFT_ATTEN_CUSTOMER A     --客户信息关注表
JOIN FB_FAITH_EXECUTE_PERSON B

parameters.name: 企业出现中风险行政处罚-限期补办手续信息结果值

processors.description: 取行政处罚接口，处罚决定日期为近5年，且处罚类别为【限期补办手续】的条目数>=1，取‘处罚事由’、‘事件时间’和‘发布时间’字段
processors.script:
ESql.withInstance(EngineSpringApplicationContextUtil.getDefaultDataSource()){ sql->
    sql.withTransaction{
        def exe_sql='''
        
INSERT INTO T_AFT_WARN_INFO 
(
ID,                    --ID
RULE_CODE,             --规则编码  
TASK_SEQNO,            --跑批批次
LESSEE_ID,             --承租人ID
ASSO_ID,               --关联人ID
ASSO_TYPE,             --关联人类型
WARN_TIME,             --预警时间
WARN_DESC              --预警详情
)
SELECT
SYS_GUID() ID  --ID
,'R003030001' RULE_CODE --规则编码
,(SELECT MAX(TASK_SEQNO)+1 FROM T_AFT_WARN_INFO WHERE RULE_CODE='R003030001') TASK_SEQNO --跑批批次
,A.LESSEE_ID --承租人ID
,A.ASSO_ID --关联人ID
,A.ASSO_TYPE --关联人类型
,SYSTIMESTAMP WARN_TIME --预警时间
,'标题：'|| B.TITLE || '，作出行政处罚决定日期为' || B.PUNISH_DECISION_DATE || '，事件时间为' || B.EVENT_DATE || '，处罚事由为' || C.PUNISH_REASON WARN_DESC --预警详情
FROM T_AFT_ATTEN_CUSTOMER A     --客户信息关注表
JOIN FB_PUNISH B           
ON A.ASSO_COMPANY_ID = B.COMPANY_ID
JOIN FB_PUNISH_TABLE C 
ON B.COMPANY_ID=C.COMPANY_ID
AND TO_CHAR(B.FD_CREATE_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') = TO_CHAR(C.FD_CREATE_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD')
AND C.PUNISH_TYPE_ONE LIKE '%限期补办手续%'
JOIN (SELECT COMPANY_ID,COUNT(*) FROM FB_PUNISH_TABLE WHERE PUNISH_TYPE_ONE LIKE '%限期补办手续%'
AND TO_CHAR(FD_CREATE_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') =TO_CHAR(SYSDATE,'YYYY-MM-DD')
GROUP BY COMPANY_ID HAVING COUNT(*) >= 1) D 
ON C.COMPANY_ID=D.COMPANY_ID
WHERE TO_CHAR(B.FD_CREATE_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') =TO_CHAR(SYSDATE,'YYYY-MM-DD')
AND ADD_MONTHS(TRUNC(SYSDATE,'DD'),-60) <= TO_DATE(SUBSTR(B.PUNISH_DECISION_DATE,1,10),'YYYY-MM-DD')
AND A.IS_ATTEN='Y' 
AND ADD_MONTHS(TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(SYSDATE,'YYYY-MM-DD'),'YYYY-MM-DD'),-6) <= TO_DATE(SUBSTR(B.PUNISH_DECISION_DATE,1,10),'YYYY-MM-DD')
        
        '''.toString();
        sql.execute(exe_sql);
    }
}

parameters.name: 第一大股东变更结果值

processors.description: 取工商变更接口，‘变更事项’中‘投资人变更’则用变更后投资人名称，去接口‘股东信息’中按‘持股比’找出最大股东，或出现‘投资总额变更’时直接找所有股东中‘持股比’最大的
processors.script:
ESql.withInstance(EngineSpringApplicationContextUtil.getDefaultDataSource()){ sql->
    sql.withTransaction{
        def exe_sql='''
        
INSERT INTO T_AFT_WARN_INFO 
(
ID,                    --ID
RULE_CODE,             --规则编码  
TASK_SEQNO,            --跑批批次
LESSEE_ID,             --承租人ID
ASSO_ID,               --关联人ID
ASSO_TYPE,             --关联人类型
WARN_TIME,             --预警时间
WARN_DESC              --预警详情
)
SELECT
 SYS_GUID() ID  --ID
,'R001001002' RULE_CODE --规则编码
,(SELECT MAX(TASK_SEQNO)+1 FROM T_AFT_WARN_INFO WHERE RULE_CODE='R001001002') TASK_SEQNO --跑批批次
,A.LESSEE_ID --承租人ID
,A.ASSO_ID --关联人ID
,A.ASSO_TYPE --关联人类型
,SYSTIMESTAMP WARN_TIME --预警时间
,'第一大股东发生变更，变更后第一大股东为' || B.SHAREHOLDER || '，持股比' || TO_CHAR(B.SHAREHOLD_RATIO *100,'fm999990.99999') || '%'  WARN_DESC --预警详情
FROM T_AFT_ATTEN_CUSTOMER A     --客户信息关注表
JOIN --当天的最大股东
 (SELECT COMPANY_ID, SHAREHOLDER,SHAREHOLD_RATIO
  FROM FB_SHAREHOLDER_INFO 
 WHERE (COMPANY_ID, SHAREHOLD_RATIO) IN
       (SELECT COMPANY_ID, MAX(SHAREHOLD_RATIO) AS SHAREHOLD_RATIO
          FROM FB_SHAREHOLDER_INFO
         WHERE TO_CHAR(FD_CREATE_DATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') =
               TO_CHAR(SYSDATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD')
         GROUP BY COMPANY_ID) 
AND TO_CHAR(FD_CREATE_DATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') =
       TO_CHAR(SYSDATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD')
) B
ON A.ASSO_COMPANY_ID = B.COMPANY_ID
JOIN --前一天的最大股东
(SELECT COMPANY_ID, SHAREHOLDER,SHAREHOLD_RATIO
  FROM FB_SHAREHOLDER_INFO 
 WHERE (COMPANY_ID, SHAREHOLD_RATIO) IN
       (SELECT COMPANY_ID, MAX(SHAREHOLD_RATIO) AS SHAREHOLD_RATIO
          FROM FB_SHAREHOLDER_INFO
         WHERE TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(FD_CREATE_DATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD'),'YYYY-MM-DD') =
               TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(SYSDATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD'),'YYYY-MM-DD')-1
         GROUP BY COMPANY_ID) 
AND TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(FD_CREATE_DATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD'),'YYYY-MM-DD') =
               TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(SYSDATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD'),'YYYY-MM-DD')-1
) C 
ON B.COMPANY_ID=C.COMPANY_ID
AND B.SHAREHOLDER <> C.SHAREHOLDER
WHERE A.IS_ATTEN='Y'

        
        '''.toString();
        sql.execute(exe_sql);
    }
}

processors.description: 近12个月内股东变更次数累计>=3，取工商变更接口，【变更事项】取值为（投资人变更）
processors.script:
ESql.withInstance(EngineSpringApplicationContextUtil.getDefaultDataSource()){ sql->
    sql.withTransaction{
        def exe_sql='''
        
INSERT INTO T_AFT_WARN_INFO
  (ID,
   RULE_CODE,
   TASK_SEQNO,
   LESSEE_ID,
   ASSO_ID,
   ASSO_TYPE,
   WARN_TIME,
   WARN_DESC)
SELECT SYS_GUID() ID, --ID
         'R001001003' RULE_CODE, --规则编码
         (SELECT MAX(TASK_SEQNO) + 1
            FROM T_AFT_WARN_INFO
           WHERE RULE_CODE = 'R001001003') TASK_SEQNO, --跑批批次
         AC.LESSEE_ID, --承租人ID
         AC.ASSO_ID, --关联人ID
         AC.ASSO_TYPE, --关联人类型
         SYSTIMESTAMP WARN_TIME, --预警时间
         '变更日期为' || ICW.CHANGE_DATE || '，变更事项为' || ICW.CHANGE_CONTENT ||
         '，变更前内容为' || ICW.CHANGE_BEFORE || '，变更后内容为' || ICW.CHANGE_AFTER WARN_DESC --预警详情
    FROM T_AFT_ATTEN_CUSTOMER AC
   INNER JOIN (SELECT IC.COMPANY_ID
                 FROM FB_INDUSTRIAL_CHANGE IC
                WHERE TRIM(IC.CHANGE_CONTENT) LIKE '%投资人变更%'
                  AND TO_CHAR(IC.FD_CREATE_DATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') =
                      TO_CHAR(SYSDATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD')
                  AND TO_DATE(SUBSTR(IC.CHANGE_DATE, 0, 10), 'YYYY-MM-DD') >=
                      ADD_MONTHS(TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(SYSDATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD'),
                                         'YYYY-MM-DD'),
                                 -12)
                GROUP BY IC.COMPANY_ID
               HAVING COUNT(*) >= 3) TEMP
      ON AC.ASSO_COMPANY_ID = TEMP.COMPANY_ID
   INNER JOIN FB_INDUSTRIAL_CHANGE ICW
      ON TEMP.COMPANY_ID = ICW.COMPANY_ID
   WHERE AC.IS_ATTEN = 'Y' AND TRIM(ICW.CHANGE_CONTENT) LIKE '%投资人变更%'
                  AND TO_DATE(SUBSTR(ICW.CHANGE_DATE, 0, 10), 'YYYY-MM-DD') >=
                      ADD_MONTHS(TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(SYSDATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD'),
                                         'YYYY-MM-DD'),
                                 -12)
     AND TO_CHAR(ICW.FD_CREATE_DATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') =
         TO_CHAR(SYSDATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD')
        
        '''.toString();
        sql.execute(exe_sql);
    }
}

	   WHERE TRIM(CHANGE_CONTENT) LIKE '%高管变更%'
       AND TO_CHAR(FD_CREATE_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') =TO_CHAR(SYSDATE,'YYYY-MM-DD')
       AND ADD_MONTHS(TRUNC(SYSDATE,'DD'),-12) <= TO_DATE(CHANGE_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD')
    GROUP BY COMPANY_ID HAVING COUNT(CHANGE_CONTENT)>=3) C      
ON B.COMPANY_ID = C.COMPANY_ID
WHERE A.IS_ATTEN='Y' 
AND TO_CHAR(B.FD_CREATE_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD') =TO_CHAR(SYSDATE,'YYYY-MM-DD')
        
        '''.toString();
        sql.execute(exe_sql);
    }
}

processors.description: 年报接口中企业经营状态<>“在营/开业"且出现在经营异常接口中
processors.script:
ESql.withInstance(EngineSpringApplicationContextUtil.getDefaultDataSource()){ sql->
    sql.withTransaction{
        def exe_sql='''
        
INSERT INTO T_AFT_WARN_INFO (ID,RULE_CODE,TASK_SEQNO,LESSEE_ID,ASSO_ID,ASSO_TYPE,WARN_TIME,WARN_DESC)
SELECT 
    SYS_GUID() ID,--ID
    'R001002001' RULE_CODE,--规则编码
    (SELECT MAX(TASK_SEQNO)+1 FROM T_AFT_WARN_INFO WHERE RULE_CODE='R001002001') TASK_SEQNO,--跑批批次
    AC.LESSEE_ID,--承租人ID
    AC.ASSO_ID,--关联人ID
    AC.ASSO_TYPE,--关联人类型
    SYSTIMESTAMP WARN_TIME,--预警时间
    '企业经营状态为'||ARB.ENTERPRISE_OPERATE_STATUS || '，或' || AO.ABNORMAL_DATE || '列入经营异常' || '，异常原因为' || AO.ABNORMAL_REASON WARN_DESC --预警详情
FROM
    T_AFT_ATTEN_CUSTOMER AC 
    INNER JOIN FB_ABNORMAL_OPERATION AO ON AC.ASSO_COMPANY_ID=AO.COMPANY_ID
    INNER JOIN FB_ANNUAL_REPORT_BASE_INFO ARB ON AC.ASSO_COMPANY_ID=ARB.COMPANY_ID
WHERE AC.IS_ATTEN='Y' AND TO_CHAR(AO.FD_CREATE_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD')=TO_CHAR(SYSDATE,'YYYY-MM-DD')
AND TO_CHAR(ARB.FD_CREATE_DATE,'YYYY-MM-DD')=TO_CHAR(SYSDATE,'YYYY-MM-DD')
AND TRIM(ARB.ENTERPRISE_OPERATE_STATUS) NOT IN ('在营','开业') 
        
        '''.toString();
        sql.execute(exe_sql);
    }
}

processors.script:
ESql.withInstance(EngineSpringApplicationContextUtil.getDefaultDataSource()){ sql->

        def exe_sql='''
        
INSERT INTO T_AFT_WARN_INFO 
(
ID,                    --ID
RULE_CODE,             --规则编码  
TASK_SEQNO,            --跑批批次
LESSEE_ID,             --承租人ID
ASSO_ID,               --关联人ID
ASSO_TYPE,             --关联人类型
WARN_TIME,             --预警时间
WARN_DESC              --预警详情
)
SELECT
 SYS_GUID() ID  --ID
,'R001007001' RULE_CODE --规则编码
,(SELECT MAX(TASK_SEQNO)+1 FROM T_AFT_WARN_INFO WHERE RULE_CODE='R001007001') TASK_SEQNO --跑批批次
,A.LESSEE_ID --承租人ID
,A.ASSO_ID --关联人ID
,A.ASSO_TYPE --关联人类型
,SYSTIMESTAMP WARN_TIME --预警时间
,'发布期为' || B.PUBLIC_PERIOD || '，税务机关为' || B.TAX_AUTHORITY || '，认定时间为' || B.IDENTIFICATION_TIME WARN_DESC --预警详情

        '''.toString();

}
